    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In ..3.. nomine. Notjcia brevis memoratorio in corum presencia bonorum
                        hominum qui supter leguntur. Idest <persName><name ref="Waldegarius"
                                >Vvalcherio</name></persName> [..17..] cives <placeName
                            ref="#places/191">Regienses</placeName> seo <persName><name
                                ref="Garifusus">Garifuso</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Waldegarius">Vvalcheri</name></persName> seo <persName><name
                                ref="Rotelmus">Rotelmo</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannacis">Iohanaci</name></persName> et
                            <persName>G[..2..]dulfo</persName> de [.. 11..]e[..3..] et
                                <persName><name ref="Rotarius">Roterio</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Salian #Witness"><name ref="Gotefredus"
                            >Cotefredo</name></persName> et <persName key="#Salian #Witness"><name
                                ref="Madaluuinus">Madoloino</name></persName> genere <rs
                            key="#Salian">Francorum</rs>, <persName key="#Scabini #Witness"><name
                                ref="Lupicinus">Lupicino</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Scabini #Witness"><name ref="Dondus">Dondo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scavinis</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Witness #Scabini #vassusOf" ref="#places/1504"
                        >Solaria</placeName>. [..9.. sca]vino de <placeName key="#Scabini"
                            ref="#places/1511">Sorbaria</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Trasmundus">Trasemundo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        germani de Sorbaria, <persName key="#Scabini #Witness"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Paulus">Pauloni</name></persName> scavino et [..7..] filius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Ermenaldus">Ermenaldo</name></persName> seo et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Armatus">Armatus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Peredeo">Peredeo</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Lupicinus">Lupicino</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/1525">Siculo</placeName> seu <persName><name
                                ref="Landeradus">Landerado</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Other_clerics #Witness"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs> [..
                            13<persName>..]tic[..2..]</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ursus">Urso</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Leo"
                                >Leo</name></persName> et reliquis plures. In istorum
                        superscriptorum presencia coniunserunt se domno <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Monasteries #Abbots"
                            ref="#people/1242">Teoderico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots ">abbas</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities" ref="#people/1244"
                            >Aimo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">avocato</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15"><orgName
                                key="#Abbots #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Monasteries #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object"
                                ref="#juridical_persons/47">Nonantole</orgName></placeName> cum
                            <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/1243"
                            >Gandulfo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Mauringus">Mauringi</name></persName> super
                        ipsas ter[.. 11 ..]coras vel <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs> illa qui es
                        posita in loco prope fluvio qui fuit <rs key="#Rivers">Moclena</rs> qui
                        vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object"
                            >Diritann[..6..]</placeName> ipso suprascripto Gandulfo gastaldio malo
                        ordine detenebat, da mane parte fluvio qui dicitur Moclena et [..6..] fluvio
                        Lama, uno capite tenente in limite <placeName>Polito</placeName>, et de
                        suptus capite tenente in loco <placeName
                            key="#Wine #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object"
                            >Cornio</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Wine #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object"
                            >Fracseno</placeName> atque in <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Wine #Hay/fodder #Fruits/vegetables #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalia #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object"
                            ref="#places/1541"><geogName
                                key="#Casalia #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object"
                                ref="#estates/1115">Modenula</geogName></placeName> hanc Lodoria
                        intrante Moclena. Ipsas suprascripta res per uno fuste que in manibus
                        tenebat ipso Gandulfo s[..2..] revestivit et retradavit ad iura superscripto
                        monasterio Nonantole in mano domni Teoderici abbati et Aimoni avocato ipsius
                        monasterii quitquit in ista superscripta coerencia detenebat. Prima <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">masaricia</rs> es recta per <persName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name ref="Ursus"
                            >Urso</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Gundalpertus"
                                >Gundevertj</name></persName>, secunda masaricia qui es recta per
                            <persName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name ref="Rodemundus"
                                >Rodemundo</name></persName>, tercia masaricia qui es recta per
                            <persName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name ref="Stabilis"
                                >Stabile</name></persName>, c[..10..]tjctores [..2..] curtjs, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortjs</rs>, areis, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>,
                        terris, canpis, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratjs</rs>, silvis, cum omnia
                        iacencia et pertjnencia sua seo et predicto [..10..] Gandulfo gastaldio
                        filio quondam Mauringi malo ordine detenebat, ex terra aratoria ad racione
                        facta [..16.. e]x omnibus qualiter superius legitur ad presenti die per
                        fuste que suis manibus detenebat ipso suprascripto Gandulfo filio Maurin[gi
                        ..13..] omnes ipsas res que ad sua manibus detenebant in manum domni
                        Teoderici abbatj et Aimoni avocato ipsius monasterii iura et proprietatem
                        iam dictj monasterii. Et pro ipsa tradicione recepit ego suprascripto
                        Gandulfo vvidredono guantj[..3..] et [..4..vvar]pivit et vobis propria
                        vestitura fecit. Et si ego Gandulfo filio quondam Mauringi aut ullus de
                        filiis vel heredibus meis contra hanc mea tradicione qualiter superius
                        legitur alico tempore causare aut removere presunserimus per nobis aut per
                        sumisa persona tunc conponamus vobis domni Teoderici abbatj tuisque
                        successoribus ad parte suprascripti monasterii vestri pena nomine in argento
                        [..7..]tj sup stipulacione supnisxsa et pos pena soluta hanc mea tradicione
                        in sua permanead firmitate. Tempore domni 
                            Ludovici magno <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatore</rs> augusto in Christi nomine anno vigesimo tercio, die
                        nono mense iunio, [indicione ..2..] feliciter. Signum + mano Gandulfi filio
                        quondam Mauringi qui ista tradicione seo investicione fecit et mano sua
                        posuit. [+ Ego <persName key="#Witness">..4..]scano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness">ibi fuit</rs>. + Ego <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"
                                ><name ref="Iohannacis">Ioanace</name></persName> scavino ibi fui.
                        Signa ++ manibus Lupicini, Dondoni et <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"
                                ><name>Agifri</name></persName> scavini qui ibi fuerunt et manibus
                        sue posuerunt. Signa +++ manibus Trasemundi seo et Petroni et Iohanni qui
                        ibi fuerunt et mano posuerunt. Signa ++ manibus Armatus et Lupicini qui ibi
                        fuerunt et mano posuerunt. + Ego Petrus interfuit. + Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Danihel">Danihel</name></persName> ibi fui. +
                        Ego Urso ibi interfui. Signa ++ manibus Cotefrido et Madoloino genere
                        Francorum qui ibi fuerunt et mano sue posuerunt. [Signa ++ manibus <persName
                            key="#Witness">..9..]drie</persName> seo Peredei filio quondam Iohanni
                            <rs key="#vassusOf">vasallo</rs> de Solaria qui ibi fuerunt et mano sue
                        posuerunt. + <rs key="#Writer">Scripsi</rs> ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Ildeprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> hunc notjcia brevis et ibi interfuit. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
